  "body": "Consider the expression:\r\n```\r\n-a^b\r\n```\r\nFor written mathematics the convention is to interpret this as follows:\r\n```\r\n-(a^b)\r\n```\r\nHowever PromQL will interpret it as\r\n```\r\n(-a)^b\r\n```\r\n\r\n__To be discussed:__ Should PromQL keep the existing behaviour that might be not expected by users or change it to follow mathematical conventions, at the risk of breaking existing queries?",
